%h3 Dependencies

%p Please note that Netty has <em>no mandatory external dependencies</em>. JDK 1.5 (1.6 for Netty 4.x) or above is all that you need to run Netty.

%h3 Getting notified on a new release

%p You can either subscribe to <a href="../news/index.html">our official blog</a> or follow <a href="https://twitter.com/netty_project">@netty_project</a> at Twitter.

%h3 Downloading from the Maven central repository

%p Add the following dependency section to your <tt>pom.xml</tt>:

%pre.brush:xml
  :escaped
    <dependencies>
      ...
      <dependency>
        <groupId>io.netty</groupId>
        <artifactId>netty</artifactId> <!-- Use 'netty-all' for 4.0 or above -->
        <version>X.Y.Z.Q</version>
        <scope>compile</scope>
      </dependency>
      ...
    </dependencies>

